ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectPark Downsview Inc. - Toronto Hydro ** Granting of an Easement **
PrecisOrder authorizing PARC DOWNSVIEW PARK INC. to grant an easement to TORONTO HYDRO in order to install, operate and maintain an electrical transformer on a 76 square meter piece of land located on the Park's property directly off of Keele Street in Toronto, Ontario.
